.Averaging in the 0 - 700 keV interval was made in
three steps: I-1 -> 0-20 keV, I-2 -> 20 - 100 keV
and I-3 -> 100 - 700 keV. Step I-2 corresponds to the
measured values. I-1 and I-3 are taken from calculated
results normalized to the present measurements

included in the quoted uncertainty since it cancels
